<h1>The Practice</h1>

<p>The Ho System is a third path between “spend years learning to code, then build” and
“just prompt better, understanding optional.” You genuinely learn while actually building —
using AI not as a teacher or a contractor but as an implementation partner whose work you
direct, evaluate, and understand. The human keeps architectural authority; the AI handles
implementation; the human understands enough to evaluate what gets built.</p>

